To run particle codes seperately from abid bot main code, please follow these steps.

1. Copy particles.mon file into misc folder
2. Run ./makeparts.awk <path to misc folder> (without <>)
   You can find the full path by using pwd command in terminal
3. Type in the actual value for each argument in particlePicker.py
	bigTimeStep = dt between two frames
	first_time = name of the first file in dat folder, something like '00970.10526316000'
	root_dir = "path to particle_code folder"
4. Run python particlePicker.py
